snippet.title: Call of Duty: Warzone Mobile Limited Release Australia
snippet.description:
Get ready to drop in, Australia!

We are thrilled to share that our first Limited Release is now available on the Google Play Store in Australia only with an iOS option coming soon.

🌐Pre-reg on Google Play or Pre-Order on the App Store for free now: https://www.callofduty.com/warzonemobile

Follow us for all the latest intel:
Facebook: https://facebook.com/CODWarzoneMobile/ 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/WarzoneMobile
Instagram: https://instagram.com/codwarzonemobile/
